snippet.title: The Arcade - PlayStation 2 Gameplay
snippet.description:
Developed by Aqua Pacific, this PAL-only shovelware game was published by Oxygen Interactive and it somehow made its way onto the UK PlayStation Store on PS3 as a "PS2 Classic".

The Arcade [PS2 Game] (C) Oxygen Interactive
Captured via PCSX2
